popt4jlib.LocalSearch

Class IdentitySearchOptimizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • popt4jlib.LocalSearch.IdentitySearchOptimizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, LocalOptimizerIntf, OptimizerIntf

    public class IdentitySearchOptimizer
extends java.lang.Object
implements LocalOptimizerIntf
    class implements a no-search local search that always returns the argument passed to it, along with its evaluation result. Useful when no local search is needed.
